Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.83,0:00:48.54,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.21,0:00:57.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:01:04.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.43,0:01:14.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.44,0:01:19.70,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.70,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.93,0:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孩子們會不會太晚回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是在森林中迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.74,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況那座森林裏 不是聽說住著可怕的巫婆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.28,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 好擔心 我真的好擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不好的預感成真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢索與葛麗泰在漆黑的森林裏迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥 我好害怕喔～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.49,0:02:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.59,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順風聞得到很好吃的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是人類小孩的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天難得可以吃頓大餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒把感情放進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重頭再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.25,0:02:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第五話  枯葉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 葛麗泰 我會打倒巫婆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這裏由我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-幹嘛啦\N-壬生屋 別出風頭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別碰我 真是不純潔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 我要對你這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-真不純潔 不要靠近我\N-精華 小祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以這樣玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.51,0:03:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過話說回來 都當高中生了\N沒想到還要表演布偶劇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是田邊堅持要做的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是附屬小學的小鬼會來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也不會對布偶劇有興趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子都很純真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他們一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.83,0:03:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們弄到這麼晚才辛苦呢 明明是布偶劇卻要站著練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.41,0:03:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確 班長還說這樣比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得他意外地認真呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在都還在幫那笨蛋三人組特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不覺得特訓會有用就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.22,0:03:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說表演的好壞 光是角色分配就有問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會把瀧川跟壬生屋配對當主角呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是配對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且雖說巫婆要兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.54,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論搭檔是誰 我一定會好好演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好 一點都不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要演爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼說 主角應該都是我跟小舞吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都已經這麼決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想要偶爾吃點肉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真從容啊 漢索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再說了 其實我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然要演 就應該演帥氣的英雄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少也要是怪盜羅賓漢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水 我們交換吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是交換角色啊 能跟小舞搭檔的只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.67,0:05:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誤食毒蘋果而沉眠的小舞 將由偶然經過的王子我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這根本是另外一部戲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨戶口 你太不純潔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.18,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.49,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壬生屋 小心會被傳染變笨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.93,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果這次的角色分配 根本沒有人樂意接受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.43,0:05:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還真想知道角色這麼分配的理由呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說理由嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.81,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水跟芝村的默契是不夠 也不用特意讓他們扮演巫婆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是故意的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.59,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得兩人一起做事的話 感情就會變得比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊破數11 命中率70%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 剛剛那樣感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.13,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我通通都有瞄準 是你發射的時機不夠好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過感覺比以前好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(不只是演戲 在戰鬥上 也希望速水跟芝村默契變好)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底走了多久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人終於來到了一間屋子前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葛麗泰 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這間屋子是用糖果做的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來好好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個笨小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.49,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為了吸引你們過來 所以特地做的房子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢索與葛麗泰不斷地吃著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這面牆是用海綿蛋糕做的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 這個屋頂是冰糖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們就慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.65,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到你們吃得白白胖胖 就換成我要吃你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表演得還蠻不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天正式上場時也能這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.16,0:08:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巫婆終於等不及了 想要把葛麗泰推到爐灶裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 到爐灶裏去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼進去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨 爐灶入口這麼大 只要像這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.55,0:08:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱～救命啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.95,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要～救命啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.07,0:09:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨手笨腳的傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壞巫婆就這麼被消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快開始、快開始啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不開始嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快開始、快開始啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣還能說小孩純真嗎 田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-準備好了吧\N-好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急廣播、緊急廣播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5121部隊請立即準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重複一次 5121部隊請立即準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不開始嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點開始啦 要開天窗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.71,0:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位再等一下好不好 求求你們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在也只能中止演出了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.69,0:11:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 當個乖孩子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 真是抱歉啦
